==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tercentenary
<hw>Ter*cen"te*na*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ter</ets> thirce + E. <ets>centenary</ets>.]</ety> <def>Including,
or relating to, an interval of three hundred years.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>The three hundredth anniversary of any event;
also, a celebration of such an anniversary.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tercet</ent>⟦br⟧
